org.chronos.chronograph.internal.impl.transaction

Class GraphTransactionContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.chronos.chronograph.internal.impl.transaction.GraphTransactionContext

  • public class GraphTransactionContext
extends java.lang.Object
    The GraphTransactionContext keeps track of the elements which have been modified by client code.

    A TransactionContext is always associated with a ChronoGraphTransaction that contains the context. The context may be cleared when a ChronoGraphTransaction.rollback() occurs on the owning transaction.
